aspose.cells
Class SaveFormat

Utility class containing constants. Represents the format in which the workbook is saved.

Field Summary
const  NumberCSV
           Represents a CSV file.
const  NumberXLSX
           Represents an xlsx file.

           Represents an xlsm file which enable macros.

           Represents an xlsb file.
const  NumberAUTO
